I don't really see anything wrong with the header file that you are using. Does test/test:test_run depend on the required kernel libaries? One way to verify this is to change tensorflow/core/kernels/constant_op.cc to add a compilation error around the REGISTER_KERNEL_BUILDER calls for Placeholder, then build to see whether it gets rebuilt in that case.

body:
I don't really see anything wrong with the header file that you are using.

Does test/test:test_run depend on the required kernel libaries?  One way to
verify this is to change tensorflow/core/kernels/constant_op.cc to add a
compilation error around the REGISTER_KERNEL_BUILDER calls for Placeholder,
then build to see whether it gets rebuilt in that case.
